data.description: Stunning, custom built, Parade of Homes award winner w/ amazing Sandia Mountain views! Luxurious details throughout w/ numerous high-end upgrades! Enter the open foyer flanked by a spiral staircase & high ceilings. Gourmet kitchen w/ Wolf Sub-Zero appliances, granite counters & custom cabinets opening to a grand living room w/ a 2-story stone fireplace. Brazilian wood floors & built-ins throughout. Primary suite has  private patio, oversize walk-in shower & free-standing tub. New hot tub on a hidden patio! Laundry upstairs & down! Amazing game room that includes a new pool/ping pong table, wet bar & deck to enjoy the beautiful Sandias. Lush landscaping in front & back. Backyard offers private, serene views overlooking the open-space. New HVAC unit 2022 & more! 3% loan can be assumed!
